enario appears including Hopf-bifurcations to incommensurately moving\nsolutions and phase-locking intervals. Stable moving breathers also survive in\npresence of weak disorder.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Dec 2013 18:43:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2014 15:06:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-22"}
