imality that the FDR smooth-threshold estimator outperforms\nthe sample mean in the common mean model $\\theta_i=\\mu$ when $|\\mu|<n^{-1/2}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Dec 2013 20:00:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-31"}
