omogeneous phantoms with EBT film the presence of the\nEBT film needs to be taken into account properly in particular for small\nfields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Dec 2013 07:58:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-06"}
